**Status check**
-->EC2 status checks are health checks performed by AWS to verify whether you ec2 instance and AWS infra are working correctly.

--types  of status checks:
1. System status check: 
--> this checks the AWS infra like physical server, AWS hypervisior, network connectivity

2. Instance Status Check:
--> this checks EC2 OS functioning

3. EBS Status Check
--> Storage connectivity

1/2 checkpass :
issue: problem is with system(AWS Infra) not your OS
solution: reboot instance

0/2 checkpass : 
issue: issue with AWS infra and instance OS
solution: stop and start instance

3/3 check pass:
--> all OK

